Jessica Jones S01E11 AKA I've Got the Blues nHD WEBrip x264-[MULVAcoded]

Jessica searches morgues for clues. Trish goes all out to keep Simpson from getting in Jessica's way. Malcom has an epiphany.

***RELEASE NOTE***
This episode is NOT in HD. nHD stands for "ninth of a Full HD frame" which is 640x360. Since this is the official term, we might as well use it.
